name: The Kind Old Mage
description:
Collectible amazing characters from a fantasy story who you would not want to enter your dream and turn it into your worst nightmare. Even those that look sweet and harmless are devilishly dangerous, manipulative and deadly...

1. The Icy Fox

2. The Fiery Gin

3. The Air Witch

4. The Earth Lizard

5. The Fire Fox

6. The Crazy Chameleon

7. The Sky Harpy

8. The Mad Hunter

9. The Octobra H. W. Mask

10. The Lava Demon

11. The Kind Old Mage
